---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import CTABanner from '../components/CTABanner.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import heroImage from '../assets/images/hero-image.jpg';
---

<Layout title="Guides & Resources - FiNAN">
  <main>
    <Navbar />
    <PageHeader
      title="Guides & Resources"
      description="Essential information and resources for Filipino healthcare professionals in the Nordic countries."
      backgroundImage={heroImage}
      backgroundAlt="Resources and guides for healthcare professionals"
    />

    <!-- Additional content sections can be added here -->
    <section class="bg-white py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6">
        <header class="max-w-2xl">
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-4xl"
          >
            Getting Started in the Nordic Countries
          </h2>
        </header>

        <div class="mt-4">
          <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
            Moving to work in the Nordic countries as a healthcare professional
            can be both exciting and challenging. Our comprehensive guides will
            help you navigate the process from initial planning to successful
            integration into your new workplace and community.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
            Whether you're considering Denmark, Finland, Iceland, Norway, or
            Sweden, each country has unique requirements, opportunities, and
            cultural considerations that are important to understand before
            making the transition.
          </p>

          <h3
            class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-3xl"
          >
            Professional Requirements
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
            Each Nordic country has specific licensing and certification
            requirements for healthcare professionals. Understanding these
            requirements early in your planning process is crucial for a smooth
            transition. We provide detailed information about credential
            recognition, language requirements, and professional registration
            processes.
          </p>

          <h3
            class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-3xl"
          >
            Cultural Integration
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
            Successful integration goes beyond professional requirements.
            Understanding Nordic workplace culture, social norms, and community
            life will help you thrive in your new environment. Our resources
            cover everything from workplace etiquette to building lasting
            relationships in your new community.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <CTABanner />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
